<title>
P&#x002F;S System Construction
</title>
<ptxt>
The power steering (P&#x002F;S) system in this vehicle reduces the driver&#8217;s effort needed in turning the steering wheel by utilizing the hydraulic pressure generated by the power steering (P&#x002F;S) pump (2) which is driven by the engine.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
It is an integral type with the rack and pinion gears and the control valve unit, hydraulic pressure cylinder unit all built in the steering gear case (1).
